messages.message: How did 5 compare to GPT-4o in your tests, is it something we plan to deploy soon?
results show marginal improvements at best; so not enough proof points to warrant an update… (keep internal)

Interesting! This has also been my experience it does not feel like a step change.

These test cases all do look quite simple docs wonder if would be any bigger difference with complex ones which require more understanding. However let’s hope there is a bigger difference with next minor release as they fix things
